Title: Embassies and Envoys
Description:
We sailed for what seemed like an eternity. I must admit there were times when I worried we would arrive too late.

But seeing all of you, united and strong, has rekindled my hope.

Before we begin planning, we must set up a base of operations here in Dornogal.
ObjectivesText: Setup your faction's embassy in Dornogal.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Find Moira in Dornogal and report back
RewardText:
Ye mean tae tell me ye have been an interior decorator this whole time an ye have been holdin' out on me?

Well done, $n.

Ye are rearrangin' me chambers when we get home, ye are.

Objectives.Text: Alliance Embassy steward found in Dornogal
